          "subject": "LinkedIn Automation: No fresh topics found this week",
          "message": "=<h2>No Fresh Topics Found</h2><p>The LinkedIn content generator could not find enough fresh AI/automation topics from RSS feeds this week.</p><p>You may want to manually add topics to the Google Sheets content calendar.</p><p><a href=\"{{ $env.LINKEDIN_SHEET_URL }}\">Open Content Calendar</a></p>",
          "options": {}
        },
        "id": "no_topics_alert",
